Redesigned and implemented edit pages of all shop item types
#Features - TourRouteInput: When modifying the route of a tour or party, a google maps preview is shown - SearchResults: Added filtering menu to search results on desktop - SearchResults: Redesigned search results on desktop + hovering animation - SearchResults: Above search results a title showing how many results were fetched is shown - User Profile: Implemented participated-tours map - Costs: Implemented costs table prototype (with cost-category and cost-value table cell components)
#Bug Fixes: - ProfilePictureForm: shouldn't throw an error anymore when linking to other image hosting sites
#Other Changes: - Refactoring: UserDataForm is now used for the sign up process _and_ the editUser page - Refactoring: Replaced hard-coded € signs with the currency pipe to make the formatting more consistent - Mock data: Updated mock data so they conform to the new data model - Removed md2 dependency (since the datepicker is now supported by angular-material)
